Note: ===================================================================
Note: MATLAB LEXER
Note: ===================================================================
Note: Lexical analysis for MATLAB (Matrix Laboratory) - scientific
Note: and engineering computing language.

Note: MATLAB is a matrix-oriented language designed for numerical
Note: computing, data analysis, algorithm development, and visualization.

Note: Key features:
Note: - Matrix/array-oriented programming (core paradigm)
Note: - Element-wise operations (.*, ./, .^, etc.)
Note: - Advanced indexing (logical, linear, subscript)
Note: - Function handles and anonymous functions
Note: - Object-oriented programming (classdef)
Note: - Vectorization and broadcasting
Note: - Graphics and plotting

Note: Part of the Translation Translation System
Note: Location: compiler/middle/gungnir/hir/translation/frontends/matlab/matlab_lexer.runa
Note: ===================================================================

Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/collections/list.runa" as ListCore

